### ============================================
### Exam Auto-Award System - Test Scenarios
### ============================================
### Use this file with REST Client extension in VS Code
### or import into Postman/Insomnia

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8083
@contentType = application/json

### ============================================
### Health Check
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications-badges/exam-integration/health

### ============================================
### Scenario 1: Score 45% - Nothing Awarded (Failed)
### ============================================
### Expected Result:
### - passed: false
### - certificationAwarded: false
### - badgeAwarded: false
### - message: "Did not pass (minimum 60% required)"

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications-badges/exam-integration/process-exam-result
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "learnerId": 2,
  "examId": 102,
  "score": 45.0,
  "maxScore": 100.0
}

### ============================================
### Scenario 2: Score 75% - Certification + Silver Badge
### ============================================
### Expected Result:
### - passed: true
### - certificationAwarded: true
### - badgeAwarded: true
### - Badge: Silver (75% threshold)
### - message: "Passed! Certification awarded. Badge awarded for high achievement!"

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications-badges/exam-integration/process-exam-result
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "learnerId": 3,
  "examId": 102,
  "score": 75.0,
  "maxScore": 100.0
}

### ============================================
### Scenario 3: Score 92% - Certification + Gold Badge
### ============================================
### Expected Result:
### - passed: true
### - certificationAwarded: true
### - badgeAwarded: true
### - Badge: Gold (90% threshold)
### - message: "Passed! Certification awarded. Badge awarded for high achievement!"

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications-badges/exam-integration/process-exam-result
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "learnerId": 4,
  "examId": 102,
  "score": 92.0,
  "maxScore": 100.0
}

### ============================================
### Scenario 4: Exactly 60% - Certification + Bronze Badge
### ============================================
### Expected Result:
### - passed: true (exactly at threshold)
### - certificationAwarded: true
### - badgeAwarded: true
### - Badge: Bronze (60% threshold)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications-badges/exam-integration/process-exam-result
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "learnerId": 5,
  "examId": 102,
  "score": 60.0,
  "maxScore": 100.0
}

### ============================================
### Scenario 5: Duplicate Prevention Test
### ============================================
### Run this twice with the same learnerId
### First call: Should award certification + badge
### Second call: Should NOT award (duplicate prevention)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications-badges/exam-integration/process-exam-result
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "learnerId": 6,
  "examId": 102,
  "score": 85.0,
  "maxScore": 100.0
}

### ============================================
### Scenario 6: Different Score Format (Fractional)
### ============================================
### Test with non-round numbers

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications-badges/exam-integration/process-exam-result
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "learnerId": 7,
  "examId": 102,
  "score": 87.5,
  "maxScore": 100.0
}

### ============================================
### Scenario 7: Different Max Score
### ============================================
### Test percentage calculation with different max score

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications-badges/exam-integration/process-exam-result
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "learnerId": 8,
  "examId": 102,
  "score": 45.0,
  "maxScore": 50.0
}

### ============================================
### Query Earned Certifications for Learner
### ============================================
### Replace {learnerId} with actual learner ID

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications-badges/earned-certifications/learner/3

### ============================================
### Query Earned Badges for Learner
### ============================================
### Replace {learnerId} with actual learner ID

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications-badges/earned-badges/learner/3

### ============================================
### Validation Error Test: Missing Required Fields
### ============================================
### Expected: 400 Bad Request

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications-badges/exam-integration/process-exam-result
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "learnerId": 2
}

### ============================================
### Validation Error Test: Negative Score
### ============================================
### Expected: 400 Bad Request

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/certifications-badges/exam-integration/process-exam-result
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "learnerId": 2,
  "examId": 102,
  "score": -10.0,
  "maxScore": 100.0
}
